						<summary>

						<p><hi rend="italic">Hero-stone in a private site near the temple of Hanumān</hi></p>						

						<p>Rāmachandra—A.D. 1281.</p>						

						<p>This inscription is dated in the <hi rend="bold">12th year (?)</hi> of the reign of <hi rend="bold">Rāmachandradēva, Vishu, Śrāvaṇa ba. Ashṭami, Friday,</hi> corresponding to <hi rend="bold">A.D. 1281, August 8, Friday.</hi></p>						

						<p>It records the death of <hi rend="bold">Sura-gauḍa,</hi> probably the disciple of <hi rend="bold">Sānti-Bhaṭṭāraka.</hi></p>						

						</summary>
