<!--<h4>First Piece.</h4>-->

<p>
<lb n="1"/>svasti śrīmatu yādavanārāyaṇa <unclear>bhu</unclear>ja
<lb n="2" break="no"/>baḷaprātāpacakravartti vīrarāmacaṁdradēva rā 
</p>

<!--<h4>Second Piece.</h4>-->

<p>
<lb n="3" break="no"/>jyōdayada viṣusaṁvacharada 12 śravaṇa bāhuḷa Asṭa
<lb n="4" break="no"/>mi sukravaradalu sāṁttibhaṭṭārakara kuḍalu sura
</p>

<!--<h4>Third Piece.</h4>-->

<p>
<lb n="5" break="no"/>gauḍa suralōkaprāpta śrī
</p>

